Fetch and unpack the platforms runtimes into their corresponding
sub-dir.

Overall structure should looks like:
- runtimes/linux/i686/xulrunner/{libxul.so, etc.}
- runtimes/linux/x86_64/xulrunner/{libxul.so, etc.}
- runtimes/mac/universal/XUL.framework/{libxpcom.dylib, etc.}
- runtimes/win/32/xulrunner/{xul.dll, etc.}

